contents.desc: Heat the oven at 200 degrees. Line parchment paper and cookie trays.

Place egg whites in a stand mixer bowl fitted with a whisk and whip until stiff peaks hold  about 1-2 minutes and meringue does not slide out when bowl is turned upside.  Add in sugar, vanilla, and vinegar. Increase speed and whip until mixture forms 2 minutes in medium speed. Add the coloring in and mix for another minute. When you the meringue is free of sugar grits how will you know is when you rubbed between two fingers and no sandy feeling and the meringue holds stiff and glossy peaks, lThen In a pastry bag or zip lock large bag put the mixer in it and pipe into a heart shape on the cookie tray with parchment paper on. Place in oven for 2 hours or 120 minutes turn off the oven open the oven door and let them sit in there for 1 hour until the cookie peels off sheet.  Allow them to cool down and enjoy.          #meringue #meringuecookies #cookies #lollipop #fyp #fyp„Ç∑ #recipe #easyrecipe #cookie #cookies
